            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Here lies Nonios Pi[--], a carpenter. A column and Fate snatched away this once most handsome man, who left behind the most wretched grief for his father. He lived 22 years.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>A verse distych begins midway through line 3.</p>
            </div>
